<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e207864c25309204499537b94e8bfe823ce7c540","tid":359114,"uid":83511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有fd做過 佢同我講守夜好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做唔過 <br />\n除非你撚枝電筒撚得好出色</blockquote><br />\n翻生恐龍館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"61253d5c276f09aea7315659376e6772f2691e3c","tid":359114,"uid":83511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"fed9ae2aca3ac4ca8be68df281931a4aa309013b","tid":359114,"uid":87613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>遲d要in呢份工，有冇巴絲知完左約有冇得續？係咪真係做打雜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做緊打雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係做打雜？我見香土2010有人咁講:<br />\n除非你係好頹或無咩大志的人,如果唔係千奇唔好做呢份工!入到去做,會當你打雜咁,完全學唔到野.裏面職級分得好清楚,唔係你做的野掂都唔會掂到,重要野唔會俾呢個位既人做.仲有,呢個位係無得續的,合約完之後出番出面,第一出面私人公司未必會承認個資歷,因為個位真係無野學到,第二呢個位好頹,做耐左我肯定你唔會適應到出面既世界----我宜家做緊類似的位,煩緊點走出去,之前呢個位的人都只係做左兩個月就走人<br />\n<br />\n是咪仲適用於依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知你返咩博物館啦, 不過我個間就咩都要幫下手, 學唔學到嘢就睇同事肯唔肯教你同自己有無心學啦,可以坐足全日玩手機又可以忙足全日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfceec011efdeaff53efd2f8651efafb350903e","tid":359114,"uid":91620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"唔好做 除非你有父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdf322d2e501df6c377e2b5fb4c105c8628a798","tid":359114,"uid":83511,"like":0,"dislik